<TabItem label="Python">

```python
import requests

response = requests.get('https://api.echovalue.dev/kv/default/mykey',
  headers={'x-token': 'mytoken'}
)
print('Cost:', response.headers.get('x-cost'))
print('Balance:', response.headers.get('x-balance'))
